      <title>安装教程</title>
      <link href="/2018/11/10/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
      <url>/2018/11/10/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="网易云音乐修复"><a href="#网易云音乐修复" class="headerlink" title="网易云音乐修复"></a>网易云音乐修复</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo gedit /etc/sudoers</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改/etc/sudoers文件，加一行：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">YOURNAME ALL = NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/netease-cloud-music</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>YOURNAME为你登录的用户名<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo gedit /usr/share/applications/netease-cloud-music.desktop</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>修改Exec=netease-cloud-music %U 为 Exec=sudo netease-cloud-music %U, 这样点击网易云音乐图标就是以管理员权限启动的了，且不用输入密码了。<br>于此同时设置root/admin等没有密码登录</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="终端美化"><a href="#终端美化" class="headerlink" title="终端美化"></a>终端美化</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install zsh</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install git </span><br><span class="line">sh -c &quot;$(wget https://raw.github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/master/tools/install.sh -O -)&quot;</span><br><span class="line">chsh -s /bin/zsh</span><br><span class="line">     echo $SHELL     #查看当前shell</span><br><span class="line">     cat /etc/shells  #查看系统已安装的shell</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-autosuggestions /home/.oh-my-zsh/plugins/zsh-autosuggestions</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting.git /home/.oh-my-zsh/plugins/home/.oh-my-zsh/plugins/zsh-syntax-highlighting</span><br><span class="line">sudo -i</span><br><span class="line">cd /home/.oh-my-zsh/plugins</span><br><span class="line">mkdir incr</span><br><span class="line">git clone http://mimosa-pudica.net/src/incr-0.2.zsh /home/.oh-my-zsh/plugins/incr</span><br><span class="line">cat /home/.zshrc</span><br><span class="line">ZSH_THEME=&quot;ys&quot;</span><br><span class="line">ENABLE_CORRECTION=&quot;true&quot;</span><br><span class="line">COMPLETION_WAITING_DOTS=&quot;true&quot;</span><br><span class="line">plugins=( git autojump incr zsh-autosuggestions zsh-syntax-highlighting )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="微信、QQ、百度云盘等的安装"><a href="#微信、QQ、百度云盘等的安装" class="headerlink" title="微信、QQ、百度云盘等的安装"></a>微信、QQ、百度云盘等的安装</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386</span><br><span class="line">    wget -nc https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/Release.key</span><br><span class="line">    sudo apt-key add Release.key</span><br><span class="line">    sudo apt-add-repository https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/</span><br><span class="line">    sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/wszqkzqk/deepin-wine-ubuntu.git /home</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后下载相应的.deb包即可<br>安装托盘：安装ToplconPlus的gnome-shell扩展</p><h1 id="桌面美化"><a href="#桌面美化" class="headerlink" title="桌面美化"></a>桌面美化</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install gnome-tweak-tool</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install docky</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install gnome-shell-extensions</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install chrome-gnome-shell</span><br><span class="line">#下载相应的主题、图标、字体放入对应的文件即可（例如下载到/home/file/内）————Gnome-look</span><br><span class="line">cp -r /home/file/themes/ /usr/share/themes</span><br><span class="line">cp -r /home/file/icons/ /usr/share/icons</span><br><span class="line">cp -r /home/file/fonts/ /usr/share/fonts</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Grub2美化"><a href="#Grub2美化" class="headerlink" title="Grub2美化"></a>Grub2美化</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">下载主题包，Gnome Look - GRUB themes</span><br><span class="line">cd /boot/grub </span><br><span class="line">mkdir themes</span><br><span class="line">cp -r /home/file/grub/themes/ /boot/grub/themes/</span><br><span class="line">sudo gedit /etc/default/grub</span><br><span class="line">#修改GRUB_THEME=&quot;/boot/grub/themes/主题包文件夹名称/theme.txt&quot;</span><br><span class="line">sudo update-grub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="字体修复"><a href="#字体修复" class="headerlink" title="字体修复"></a>字体修复</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">下载缺失文字复制到/usr/share/fonts中</span><br><span class="line">sudo mkfontscale</span><br><span class="line">sudo mkfontdir</span><br><span class="line">sudo fc-cache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="python-修复"><a href="#python-修复" class="headerlink" title="python 修复"></a>python 修复</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install python3</span><br><span class="line">sudo update-alternatives --list python</span><br><span class="line">ls /usr/bin/</span><br><span class="line">sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python2.7 1</span><br><span class="line">sudo update-alternatives --install /usr/bin/python python /usr/bin/python3.5 2</span><br><span class="line">sudo update-alternatives --config python</span><br><span class="line">#或者sudo apt-get remove python(不建议使用)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="部分软件安装"><a href="#部分软件安装" class="headerlink" title="部分软件安装"></a>部分软件安装</h1><p>WPS、Chrome、网易云音乐、Rstudio官网下载即可。</p><p>#spyder安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt install spyder</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#GIMP安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:otto-kesselgulasch/gimp</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install gimp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#其他安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install shutter</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install gnome-mpv</span><br><span class="line">suso apt-get install axel</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install apt-fast</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#sublime-text安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:webupd8team/sublime-text-3 </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install sublime-text</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#typora的安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-key adv --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com --recv-keys BA300B7755AFCFAE</span><br><span class="line">sudo add-apt-repository &apos;deb https://typora.io/linux ./&apos; </span><br><span class="line">sudo apt update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt install typora</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="ubuntu-18-04-命令行与图形界面的切换"><a href="#ubuntu-18-04-命令行与图形界面的切换" class="headerlink" title="ubuntu 18.04 命令行与图形界面的切换"></a>ubuntu 18.04 命令行与图形界面的切换</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo gedit /etc/default/grub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到 GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT,在此行末尾输入 nomodeset<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo update-grub</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h1 id="18-04-键盘背光打开"><a href="#18-04-键盘背光打开" class="headerlink" title="18.04 键盘背光打开"></a>18.04 键盘背光打开</h1><p>建立led.sh文件，代码如下：<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#!/bin/bash - </span><br><span class="line">#===============================================================================</span><br><span class="line">#</span><br><span class="line">#          FILE: ledctrl</span><br><span class="line"># </span><br><span class="line">#         USAGE: ./ledctrl </span><br><span class="line"># </span><br><span class="line">#   DESCRIPTION: </span><br><span class="line"># </span><br><span class="line">#       OPTIONS: ---</span><br><span class="line">#  REQUIREMENTS: ---</span><br><span class="line">#          BUGS: ---</span><br><span class="line">#         NOTES: ---</span><br><span class="line">#        AUTHOR: linkscue (scue), linkscue@gmail.com</span><br><span class="line">#  ORGANIZATION: </span><br><span class="line">#       CREATED: 2014年02月13日 13时16分55秒 CST</span><br><span class="line">#      REVISION:  ---</span><br><span class="line">#===============================================================================</span><br><span class="line">​</span><br><span class="line">status=/tmp/keyboard_led_status</span><br><span class="line">if [[ $&#123;1&#125; == &quot;on&quot; ]] || [[ ! -e $&#123;status&#125; ]]; then</span><br><span class="line">    xset led named &apos;Scroll Lock&apos; &amp;&amp; echo &quot;on&quot; &gt; $&#123;status&#125;</span><br><span class="line">else</span><br><span class="line">    xset -led named &apos;Scroll Lock&apos; &amp;&amp; rm -f $&#123;status&#125;</span><br><span class="line">fi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>于 /bin中新建一个led文件，将led.sh放入文件中，于键盘中添加快捷键，命令为 bash /bin/led/led.sh,设置快捷键即可。</p><h1 id="caj文件阅读器的安装"><a href="#caj文件阅读器的安装" class="headerlink" title="caj文件阅读器的安装"></a>caj文件阅读器的安装</h1><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386</span><br><span class="line">wget -nc https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/Release.key</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-key add Release.key</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-add-repository https://dl.winehq.org/wine-builds/ubuntu/</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get update</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install --install-recommends winehq-stable</span><br><span class="line">#下载caj绿色版一般6.0可以了，运行exe文件即可。</span><br><span class="line">#设置快捷方式，命令为 wine ./XX.exe,即可。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="为知笔记的安装"><a href="#为知笔记的安装" class="headerlink" title="为知笔记的安装"></a>为知笔记的安装</h1><p>#必要软件安装<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install git</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install build-essential</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install cmake</span><br><span class="line">sudo apt-get install zlib1g-dev</span><br><span class="line">cd /home/sk</span><br><span class="line">wget http://download.qt.io/official_releases/qt/5.7/5.7.0/qt-opensource-linux-x64-5.7.0.run</span><br><span class="line">chmod +x qt-opensource-linux-x64-5.7.0.run</span><br><span class="line">./qt-opensource-linux-x64-5.7.0.run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#Clone为知笔记源代码<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /home/sk</span><br><span class="line">mkdir WizTeam</span><br><span class="line">cd WizTeam</span><br><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/WizTeam/WizQTClient.git</span><br><span class="line">cd WizQTClient</span><br><span class="line">git checkout 2.4.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#编译源代码<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo apt-get install libgl1-mesa-dev libglu1-mesa-dev</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>#运行QT，打开./WizTeam/WizQTClient/CMakeLists.txt</p><p>#运行为知笔记即可</p>]]></content>
      
      
